title: Forced to Become the Villain’s Son-in-law
description: A third-rate writer that is destined to go to hell because of it’s novel bad ending, got reincarnated in his own novel instead, reborn as the villainous son-in-law – Li Yu Guo. The battle of wits and courage between him and the original protagonist begins now… I Become A Villain In My Novel
alternative_titles: 被迫成为反派赘婿. I Become A Villain In My Novel
